<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Registration Cancelled - Event Management System</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #dc3545;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #dc3545;
        }
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .event-details {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .cancellation-info {
            background-color: #f8d7da;
            border: 1px solid #f5c6cb;
            color: #721c24;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            padding-top: 20px;
        }
        .info-box {
            background-color: #d1ecf1;
            border: 1px solid #bee5eb;
            color: #0c5460;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .highlight {
            color: #dc3545;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">Event Management System</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Registration Cancelled</h2>
            <p>Hello {{fullName}}!</p>
            <p>Your registration for the following event has been <span class="highlight">successfully cancelled</span>:</p>
            
            <div class="event-details">
                <h3>{{eventTitle}}</h3>
                <p><strong>Date:</strong> {{eventDate}}</p>
                <p><strong>Time:</strong> {{eventTime}}</p>
                <p><strong>Location:</strong> {{location}}</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="cancellation-info">
                <h4>üìã Cancellation Details</h4>
                <p><strong>Cancelled on:</strong> {{cancellationDate}}</p>
                <p><strong>Registration Token:</strong> {{registrationToken}}</p>
                <p>This registration token is now invalid and cannot be used for attendance.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="info-box">
                <h4>‚ÑπÔ∏è Important Information</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Your registration has been completely removed from our system</li>
                    <li>You will not receive any further notifications about this event</li>
                    <li>If you change your mind, you may register again (subject to availability)</li>
                    <li>No refund processing is required as this is a free event</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <p>We're sorry to see you go! If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact us.</p>
            
            <p>Thank you for your interest in our events. We hope to see you at future events!</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.</p>
            <p>&copy; 2024 Event Management System. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
